1. Add this right after:
st.title(":orange[Cfg View Control]")
st.subheader(":blue[Search for Program or View]")

Add:

if "success_message" in st.session_state:
    st.success(st.session_state["success_message"])
    del st.session_state["success_message"]
2. Replace this line:
st.success(f"{result.rows_updated} record(s) successfully updated in CFG_VW_CONTROL table..")

With this:

st.session_state["success_message"] = f"{result.rows_updated} record(s) successfully updated in CFG_VW_CONTROL table."

Keep this line as-is:

st.rerun()

That’s it. The success message will now show after rerun and stay visible.
